statements: SELECT * FROM logistics_performance;
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_date, delivery_status FROM logistics_performance ORDER BY delivery_date DESC;
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_location FROM logistics_performance WHERE delivery_status = 'Delayed';
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_time, action_taken FROM logistics_performance WHERE bottlenecks_identified IS NOT NULL;
SELECT DISTINCT delivery_status FROM logistics_performance;
SELECT * FROM logistics_performance WHERE delivery_id = 1001 ORDER BY delivery_date DESC, delivery_time ASC
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_location, delivery_status FROM logistics_performance WHERE delivery_location LIKE 'New%' AND delivery_status = 'Delayed'
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_date, delivery_location, action_taken FROM logistics_performance WHERE delivery_date >= '2022-01-01' AND bottleneliteralpencks_identified IS NOT NULL
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_status, bottlenecks_identified FROM logistics_performance ORDER BY delivery_status DESC
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_date, delivery_location, action_taken FROM logistics_performance WHERE delivery_status IN ('Delivered', 'Delayed')
SELECT * FROM bottleneck_identification;
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_date, delivery_location FROM bottleneck_identification ORDER BY delivery_date DESC;
SELECT delivery_person_id, delivery_location FROM bottleneck_identification WHERE delivery_status = 'Pending';
SELECT * FROM performance_improvement WHERE improvement_strategy = 'Route Optimization';
SELECT delivery_date, delivery_person_id, delivery_location FROM bottleneck_identification WHERE delivery_location LIKE '%City%';
SELECT * FROM bottleneck_identification WHERE delivery_location = 'New York'
SELECT delivery_date, delivery_location FROM bottleneck_identification WHERE delivery_status = 'Pending'
SELECT * FROM bottleneck_identification ORDER BY delivery_date DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_deliveries FROM bottleneck_identification
SELECT bi.delivery_id, pi.improvement_strategy FROM bottleneck_identification bi JOIN performance_improvement pi ON bi.delivery_id = pi.delivery_id
SELECT * FROM delivery_log
SELECT delivery_id, timestamp FROM delivery_log
SELECT * FROM delivery_log WHERE delivery_status = 'delivered'
SELECT delivery_id, timestamp, delivery_status FROM delivery_log ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT delivery_id, timestamp, delivery_status FROM delivery_log WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30'
SELECT delivery_id, timestamp, delivery_status FROM delivery_log WHERE delivery_status = 'delivered' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM delivery_log WHERE delivery_id IN (1, 3, 5) AND delivery_status = 'in transit';
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_status FROM delivery_log WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-10-01' AND '2022-10-31' ORDER BY delivery_id ASC;
SELECT delivery_id, timestamp FROM delivery_log WHERE delivery_status = 'failed' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM delivery_log WHERE delivery_status = 'pending' ORDER BY delivery_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM Bottlenecks;
SELECT bottleneck_id, bottleneck_description FROM Bottlenecks WHERE bottleneck_type = 'Production';
SELECT process_name, estimated_time FROM Processes WHERE estimated_time > 100;
SELECT * FROM Deliveries WHERE is_delayed = TRUE ORDER BY delivery_date DESC;
SELECT process_id, COUNT(*) AS total_deliveries FROM Performance GROUP BY process_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT * FROM Bottlenecks;
SELECT bottleneck_id, bottleneck_description FROM Bottlenecks WHERE bottleneck_type = 'Production';
SELECT process_name, process_type, estimated_time FROM Processes ORDER BY estimated_time DESC;
SELECT delivery_date, delivery_status FROM Deliveries WHERE is_delayed = TRUE;

SELECT p.performance_id, pr.process_name, b.bottleneck_description, p.performance_score FROM Performance p JOIN Processes pr ON p.process_id = pr.process_id JOIN Bottlenecks b ON p.bottleneck_id = b.bottleneck_id WHERE p.performance_score > 80 ORDER BY p.performance_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM bottlenecks;
SELECT order_id, delivery_date, bottleneck_description FROM bottlenecks WHERE id = 1;
SELECT product_name, price FROM products WHERE weight > 3.0;
SELECT personnel_name, assigned_orders, current_location FROM delivery_personnel ORDER BY assigned_orders DESC;
SELECT order_id, status FROM logistics_performance WHERE status = 'pending';
SELECT * FROM orders ORDER BY order_date DESC, customer_name ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT product_name, price FROM products WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price DESC
SELECT dp.personnel_name, dp.assigned_orders, o.customer_name FROM delivery_personnel dp INNER JOIN orders o ON dp.assigned_orders = o.order_id WHERE dp.assigned_orders <= 5
SELECT lp.order_id, lp.delivery_time, lpp.status FROM logistics_performance lp JOIN logistics_performance lpp ON lp.lp_id = lpp.lp_id
SELECT b.bottleneck_description, o.customer_name, b.delivery_date FROM bottlenecks b LEFT JOIN orders o ON b.order_id = o.order_id
